7381 G4double G4ParticleHPFastLegendre::regularEvaluate( int l , double x )
7382 {
7383  double y_pre;
7384  double y;
7385  double y_post;
7386 
7387  y_pre=1;
7388  y=x;
7389 
7390  for ( int n = 1; n<l ; n++ )
7391  {
7392  y_post = 1.0*(2*n+1)/(n+1)*x*y-1.0*n/(n+1)*y_pre;
7393  y_pre=y;
7394  y=y_post;
7395  }
7396  //G4cout << l << " " << x << " " << y << G4endl;
7397 
7398  return y;

7401 G4double G4ParticleHPFastLegendre::regularIntegrate( int l , double x )
7402 {

7404  double y;
7405  double y_post;
7406  double ydx;
7407 
7408  y_pre=1;
7409  y=x;
7410 
7411  for ( int n = 1; n<l ; n++ )
7412  {
7413  y_post = 1.0*(2*n+1)/(n+1)*x*y-1.0*n/(n+1)*y_pre;
7414  y_pre=y;
7415  y=y_post;
7416  }

7420 
7421  return -ydx;
